### TB Deaths (2003-2011)\
\
**Source**: CDC WONDER Underlying Cause of Death  \
**URL**: https://wonder.cdc.gov/deaths-by-underlying-cause.html  \
**ICD-10 Codes**: A15-A19 (Tuberculosis)  \
**Geographic Level**: State (assigned to CBSA)  \
**Temporal Coverage**: 2003-2011\
\
#### Data Processing\
\
**Assignment Method**: State-level death counts assigned to all CBSAs within each state\
- Each CBSA in a state receives the same state-level death count for a given year\
- This is a **repeated value assignment**, not a geographic aggregation\
- Does **NOT** reflect intra-state geographic variation in TB mortality\
\
**Rationale**: TB death data not available at county or CBSA level from CDC WONDER for this time period\
\
**Limitation**: Cannot distinguish geographic variation in TB mortality within states\
