## Air Quality Data\
\
### Air Pollutant Concentrations (2003-2011)\
\
**Source**: EPA Air Quality Statistics by City, 2000-2023  \
**URL**: https://www.epa.gov/air-trends/air-quality-cities-and-counties  \
**Geographic Level**: CBSA (direct)  \
**Temporal Coverage**: 2000-2023 (subset 2003-2011 used for analysis)  \
**Format**: Excel workbook with CBSA trends\
\
#### Pollutants and Metrics\
\
| Pollutant | Metric | Variable Name | Unit |\
|-----------|--------|---------------|------|\
| Carbon Monoxide (CO) | 2nd Maximum 8-hour | `co_2ndmax` | ppm |\
| Nitrogen Dioxide (NO\uc0\u8322 ) | 98th Percentile 1-hour | `no2_98thpercentile` | ppb |\
| Nitrogen Dioxide (NO\uc0\u8322 ) | Annual Mean | `no2_annualmean` | ppb |\
| Ozone (O\uc0\u8323 ) | 4th Maximum 8-hour | `o3_4thmax` | ppm |\
| Particulate Matter (PM10) | 2nd Maximum 24-hour | `pm10_2ndmax` | \uc0\u956 g/m\'b3 |\
| Fine Particulate (PM2.5) | 98th Percentile 24-hour | `pm25_98thpercentile` | \uc0\u956 g/m\'b3 |\
| Fine Particulate (PM2.5) | Weighted Annual Mean | `pm25_weightedannualmean` | \uc0\u956 g/m\'b3 |\
| Sulfur Dioxide (SO\uc0\u8322 ) | 99th Percentile 1-hour | `so2_99thpercentile` | ppb |\
\
#### Data Structure (Original)\
- **Wide format**: One row per CBSA, one column per year (2000-2023)\
- **Multiple rows per CBSA**: Separate rows for each pollutant-statistic combination\
\
#### Data Processing\
\
1. **Reshape to long**: Convert year columns (D, E, F...) to CBSA-pollutant-year rows\
2. **Create metric names**: Combine pollutant and statistic into single variable\
3. **Reshape to wide**: One row per CBSA-year with pollutant metrics as columns\
4. **Subset years**: Filter to 2003-2011 for TB analysis alignment\
