## Geographic Crosswalks\
\
### County-to-CBSA Mapping\
\
**Source**: Created from Census/OMB CBSA delineation files  \
**Format**: 5-digit county FIPS \uc0\u8594  CBSA code mapping  \
**Fields**:\
- `county_fips`: 5-digit county FIPS code (SSCCC format)\
- `state_fips`: 2-digit state FIPS code\
- `cbsa_code`: CBSA identifier\
- `cbsatitle`: CBSA name\
\
#### FIPS Code Structure\
- **State FIPS**: 2 digits (e.g., "09" = Connecticut)\
- **County FIPS**: 3 digits within state (e.g., "001" = Fairfield County)\
- **Combined**: 5-digit string (e.g., "09001")\
\
